Before you run this app, you will want to make a junk text file to play with.Once you have the file you just need to run the MPW tool and select the junk fileStandard file will come up twice, select the junk file both times.The first time the file is opened a bug is found and the file is only increased byabout one meg. (it should be increased to the size of the remaining space of the hard drive.The second time the file is opened the file is increased the the size of the remainingspace on the hard drive.It will finish by printing the results to the window.